[src:randomized-algorithms-deep/randomized-algorithm] Figure 1 gives an example of contraction of vertex *A* and *B*.
[src:randomized-algorithms-deep/randomized-algorithm] After contraction, the resulting graph may have parallel edges, but contains no self loops.
