[src:randomized-algorithms-deep/randomized-algorithm] The run time of one execution is $O(n)$ , and *n* denotes the number of vertices.
[src:randomized-algorithms-deep/randomized-algorithm] After *m* times executions of the outer loop, we output the minimum cut among all the results.
